2018-09-14  Eric Carlson  <eric.carlson@apple.com>

        Support arbitrary video resolution in getUserMedia API
        https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=178109
        <rdar://problem/35083128>

        Reviewed by Youenn Fablet.

